    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――琴乃のソロツアー、千秋楽",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "まさか琴乃のツアーですずが\nソロ曲を歌うことになるなんてな",
      "startTime": 4.8285714377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "引き受けてくれてありがとう\nでも初披露がここで本当に良かったのか？",
      "startTime": 10.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.7999999206
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "当然ですわ。むしろ、琴乃の提案には\n感謝していますのよ",
      "startTime": 17.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃のアンサーソングも私のこの曲も\nどちらも麻奈様に贈るものですから",
      "startTime": 24.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.1719954651
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "初披露するのにこれ以上の\nステージはありませんわ！",
      "startTime": 29.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "会場に来てくれるファンはもちろん……私達を見守って\nくれている麻奈様にも、喜んでいただけますわよね",
      "startTime": 36.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.0363716286
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "きっとな。二人の歌声は麻奈に届くと信じているよ\n琴乃の苦労も、すずの苦労も報われるさ",
      "startTime": 46.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃も大変だったとは聞いていたが……\nすずの方もかなり難航していたもんな",
      "startTime": 53.3333340962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.3363723915
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうですわね……でも{user}さんの\nおかげでなんとかなりましたわ",
      "startTime": 60.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_14_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "役に立ったのなら良かったよ。けど提案した時は\nあんなことになるなんて思いもしなかったけどな",
      "startTime": 67.7906987853,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}